Create a Dynamic Web Project in Eclipse
Name: HelloSpringWeb
Ensure Target Runtime is 
Apache Tomcat v10.1
Click next
Click Next
Tick on Generate web.xml
Click Finish
Open JEE Perspective if not in it.





Right click the Project 
Configure -> Convert to Maven Project

Give Details:
Group ID : com.springmvc
Artifact ID: HelloSpringWeb
Name: HelloSpringWeb
Packaging: war

Finish




